# Calendar — Visual Specification

## Architecture

All visual styling lives in `packages/css/src/calendar.css` using `@apply` for structural utilities and raw CSS for transitions, animations, and theme overrides.

---

## Class Inventory

### Wrapper & Trigger (dropdown mode)
| Class | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `.acko-cal-wrapper` | Dropdown wrapper — `relative inline-block` |
| `.acko-cal-trigger` | Trigger button — `background: var(--color-input-bg)`, `border-color: var(--color-input-border)`, `flex items-center justify-between w-full cursor-pointer` |
| `.acko-cal-trigger:hover` | Hover — `border-color: var(--color-input-hover-border)` |
| `.acko-cal-trigger-open` | Active state — `border-color: var(--color-input-focus-border)`, `box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--color-input-focus-ring)` |
| `.acko-cal-trigger-placeholder` | Placeholder — `color: var(--color-text-secondary)` |
| `.acko-cal-trigger-icon` | Calendar icon — `flex items-center`, muted color |

### Panel
| Class | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `.acko-cal-panel` | Calendar container — 340px wide, card bg, `20px` border-radius, `--shadow-md`, `--scale-16` padding |
| `.acko-cal-panel-dropdown` | Dropdown positioning — `absolute left-0`, z-index, enter animation |

### Header
| Class | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `.acko-cal-header` | Header row — `flex items-center justify-between` |
| `.acko-cal-header-label` | Month/Year label — clickable, drills into month → year picker |
| `.acko-cal-nav-btn` | Prev/Next nav — `--scale-36` square, transparent bg, hover bg |

### Day Grid
| Class | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `.acko-cal-weekdays` | 7-column grid for weekday headers |
| `.acko-cal-weekday` | Single weekday header — uppercase, muted, label-sm |
| `.acko-cal-days` | 7-column grid for day buttons (6 rows × 7 = 42 cells) |
| `.acko-cal-day` | Day button — `--scale-40` tall, full-radius, `--font-body-sm-size`, tabular-nums |

### Day States
| Class | Effect |
|---|---|
| `.acko-cal-today` | Today — `color: var(--color-cal-today-text); font-weight: 700` |
| `.acko-cal-selected` | Selected single — `bg: var(--color-cal-selected-bg); color: var(--color-cal-selected-text)` |
| `.acko-cal-range-start` | Range start — half-pill left (full-radius left, 0 right) |
| `.acko-cal-range-end` | Range end — half-pill right (0 left, full-radius right) |
| `.acko-cal-range-middle` | Range between — `bg: var(--color-cal-range-bg); border-radius: 0` |
| `.acko-cal-outside` | Dates outside current month — `color: var(--color-text-disabled)` |
| `.acko-cal-day-disabled` | Disabled — `color: var(--color-text-secondary); cursor-not-allowed` |

### Month/Year Picker
| Class | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `.acko-cal-picker-grid` | 3-column grid for month or year buttons |
| `.acko-cal-picker-cell` | Picker button — `--scale-48` tall, pill radius, `--font-body-sm-size`, 500 weight |
| `.acko-cal-picker-cell-selected` | Active pick — selected bg + text, 700 weight |
| `.acko-cal-picker-cell-current` | Current month/year — today text color, 700 weight |

---

## Animations

| Keyframe | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `acko-cal-enter` | Panel fade-in + translateY(var(--scale-8) → 0) over 150ms |

---

## Tokens Used

| Token | Usage |
|---|---|
| `--color-card-bg` | Panel background |
| `--color-card-border` | Panel border |
| `--color-input-bg` | Trigger background (`grey-white` light / `grey-750` dark) |
| `--color-input-border` | Trigger border (`grey-150` light / `grey-600` dark) |
| `--color-input-hover-border` | Trigger hover border |
| `--color-input-focus-border` | Trigger focus border |
| `--color-input-focus-ring` | Trigger focus ring `box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px` |
| `--color-primary` | Open/focus border and ring |
| `--color-primary-ring` | Focus-visible ring on nav/header |
| `--color-text-primary` | Day text, header label, picker cell text |
| `--color-text-secondary` | Weekday headers, placeholder, disabled days, trigger icon |
| `--color-text-disabled` | Outside-month days |
| `--color-cal-today-text` | Today highlight text |
| `--color-cal-selected-bg` | Selected day background |
| `--color-cal-selected-text` | Selected day text |
| `--color-cal-range-bg` | Range middle band background |
| `--color-cal-range-text` | Range middle band text |
| `--color-cal-cell-hover-bg` | Day/month/year cell hover, header label hover |
| `--shadow-md` | Panel box shadow |
| `--z-dropdown` | Dropdown panel z-index |
| `--radius-full` | Day cells, trigger, picker cells |
| `20px` | Panel corner radius |
| `--radius-lg` | Nav button, header label corners |
| `--ease-out-cubic` | Enter animation easing |

---

## Dark Theme Overrides

- Trigger: `var(--color-input-bg)` bg, `var(--color-input-border)` border
- Panel: `var(--color-surface-raised)` bg, `var(--color-border)` border

## Elevated Theme Overrides

- Trigger: Glass background with gradient border, backdrop blur, glow
- Open/focus: `var(--elevated-focus-ring)` shadow
- Panel: Glass background, gradient border, 18px blur
